35 Uppannattikādi, Kusalattika
Uppannattikādi, Kusalattika
44.
138Nauppanno nakusalo dhammo uppannassa kusalassa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo. Ārammaṇe satta, adhipatiyā cha, upanissaye satta.
139Nauppanno naakusalo dhammo uppannassa akusalassa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo. Ārammaṇe cha, adhipatiyā cha, upanissaye cha.
140Naanupanno naabyākato dhammo uppannassa abyākatassa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo…  tīṇi.
141Nauppanno naabyākato dhammo uppannassa abyākatassa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo. (Saṃkhittaṃ.)
142Hetuyā tīṇi, ārammaṇe satta, adhipatiyā cattāri, sahajāte nissaye tīṇi, upanissaye satta…pe…  avigate tīṇi.
143(Atītattikaṃ uppannattikasadisaṃ.)
